channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: WATCH: Trump Comes Up With a New Name for Biden During Rally in Virginia—It's Right on Target
Texas Supreme Court upholds state ban on gender transition treatment for minors
item.description: The Texas Supreme Court upheld the state's ban on gender transition treatment for children in an 8-1 decision after a lawsuit that argued the law harms transgender teenagers.

item.title: Iowa High Court Rules 6-Week Abortion Ban Constitutional
item.description: The Iowa Supreme Court on Friday ruled the state's six-week abortion ban is constitutional, overturning a lower-court's decision that placed a temporary injunction on the law.

item.title: Replace Joe Biden on the Democrat Ticket? Be Careful What You Wish For.
Trump says 'biggest problem' not Biden's age, 'decline,' but his policies in first appearance since debate
item.description: In his first rally following the debate, former President Trump told Virginia voters the "biggest problem" for the U.S. is not Biden's "decline" but his policies.

item.title: Gold Star Families Slam Biden's Denial of Troop Deaths
item.description: Following President Joe Biden's debate oversight regarding military deaths under his watch, members of gold star families shared their frustration with the New York Post.

item.title: Feel-Good Friday: Music Artisans Are a Dying Breed; One Town Honors Its Local Instrument Repairman
The Speaker’s Lobby: A Universal Interest
item.description: President Joe Biden and Former President Donald Trump faced off in the first Presidential Debate, showcasing the weight of live television in politics today.

item.title: Nev. Verifies Enough Signatures to Put Abortion Rights on Ballot
item.description: A ballot question to enshrine Nevada's abortion rights in the state constitution has met all of the requirements to appear in front of voters in November, the Nevada Secretary of State's office announced Friday, and Democrats across the nation hope similar measures mobilize...

item.title: Biden Goes Into Pandering Overdrive With 'Origin Story' at Stonewall Visitors Center in NYC
Cornell Law professor calls to invoke 25th Amendment after Biden's debate performance
item.description: After President Biden's weak debate performance Thursday night, Cornell Law Professor William Jacobson called for the 25th Amendment to be invoked.

item.title: Lara Trump to Newsmax: Biden on His Own a Dumpster Fire
item.description: Lara Trump, co-chair of the Republican National Committee, told Newsmax on Friday that if people saw the same debate she did Thursday night between her father-in-law, Donald Trump, and President Joe Biden, it would be game over for the Democrats.

item.title: Iowa Supreme Court Ends Injunction, Allowing 6-Week Abortion Ban to Take Effect
WATCH: Dem. Rep. snatches phone in testy airport exchange over Biden's mental clarity: 'Who owns you?'
item.description: Democratic Rep. Marcy Kaptur got into a contentious exchange with a man at a Detroit airport who asked her about President Biden's cognitive abilities after Thursday's debate.

item.title: NY Times Editorial Board: Biden Should Exit Race to Serve the Nation
item.description: President Joe Biden should exit the 2024 presidential race following a subpar debate performance against former President Donald Trump, during which he appeared on the stage as "the shadow of a great public servant," said The New York Times' editorial board.
